This is the source code used in the book Music for Geeks and Nerds.

Directories
-----------

pyknon    a copy of the pyknon library
midi      directory where the generated midi files are stored

Data files
----------

canon-crab                      theme for the crab canon
canon-quaerendo-invenietis      theme for the quaerendo invenietis canon
josquin                         theme for Josquin's canon

Source code sorted by chapter
-----------------------------

